<div .="MsoNormal">
<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN"><span style="font-size: large;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal">
<span style="font-size: large;"><span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">第二章</span><span .="mso-tab-count:2">&nbsp;</span><span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;
mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:
Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">這個帝國必須分裂</span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal">
<span style="font-size: large;"><span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">二</span><span .="mso-tab-count:1">&nbsp;</span><span .="font-family:
宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:
宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;
mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">駛不出歷史的三峽</span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal">
<span style="font-size: large;"><span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">由於千年中央專制文化和歷史的積澱&#65292;使這片土地上的人們充滿了奴性&#12290;無底線的奴性同時助長了目空一切的專制&#65292;而每一次改朝換代</span><span lang="ZH-CN">&nbsp;</span><span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">並非出於文明發展的需要&#65292;因此中國縱然富庶中國人即便富裕也仍舊愚昧不堪&#65292;因循守舊&#65292;不思進取&#12290;</span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal">
<span style="font-size: large;">1912<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">年滿清退位中華民國成立&#12290;這個號稱亞洲第一共和的國家&#65292;卻由第一任大總統袁世凱於</span>1915<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:
minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;
mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">年演出了一場復辟帝制的鬧劇&#12290;既然認為君主立憲比共和國體更適合中國國情&#65292;該請回溥儀恢復滿清才對嘛&#12290;果不其然&#12290;</span>1917<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:
minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;
mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">年張勛又搞了一次復辟&#65292;請溥儀回爐&#65292;當了十二天宣統皇帝&#12290;各地軍閥輪流坐莊的歷史最後由最大黨國民黨總裁蔣介石&#65292;以一個國家一個領袖的獨裁者面目結束&#12290;</span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal">
<span style="font-size: large;"><span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">中共</span>1949<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:
minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;
mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">年</span>9<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:
minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;
mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">月在北京召開第一屆中國人民政治協商會議&#65292;邀請了</span>46<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:
minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;
mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">個政治組織共</span>662<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:
minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;
mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">人參加&#65292;揚言&#8220;中国人民民主专政是中国工人阶级&#12289;农民阶级&#12289;小资产阶级&#12289;民族资产阶级及其他爱国民主分子的人民民主统一战线的政权&#12290;&#8221;這些參加會議的人信嗎&#65311;不知道&#12290;反正後來假裝相信也不能了&#65292;因為他們在中共一系列政治運動中死的死&#65292;殘的殘&#12290;</span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal">
<span style="font-size: large;">1976<span .="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:
minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin" lang="ZH-CN">年大獨裁者毛澤東病死&#65292;中國人民又捧出了一個小獨裁者鄧小平&#65292;手握兵權一直到死&#12290;若不是鄧小平預先設定了集體領導體制&#65292;江澤民怎肯輕易讓位&#65311;若不是江澤民早已安排習近平李克強接班&#65292;胡錦濤難道不想也連任軍委主席&#65311;不過此一時彼一時&#12290;有形勢比人強時&#65292;也有人比形勢強時&#12290;習近平顯然不理睬胡錦濤溫家寶給他預設的接班人胡春華孫政才&#65292;發動政變把孫政才拿下&#65292;其他政治老人只好束手自保&#12290;毛鄧之後&#65292;第三位獨裁者出現了&#12290;有人急了&#12290;晚了&#12290;</span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal">
