<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='http://xizongriji.blogspot.com/2018/03/blog-post_4.html'>為黨業獻終身&#65292;為萬世開太平</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-8822973934824748491' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">為黨業獻終身&#65292;為萬世開太平</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">習總日記&#65288;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">2018</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">&#65292;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">3</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">&#65292;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">5</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">&#65289;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">橫渠四句&#65306;為國家主席&#65292;為人民服務&#65292;為黨業獻終身&#65292;為萬世開太平&#12290;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">實行終身制&#65292;天下就太平了&#12290;怎麼講&#65311;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">實行了終身制&#65292;省去了選拔接班人的苦惱&#12290;至少延長了苦惱發生的頻率&#12290;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">實行了終身制&#65292;省去了底下人站隊的賭局&#12290;橫豎忠於我一人即可&#12290;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">實行了終身制&#65292;全黨全軍全國人民忠於一人&#65292;團結在一人之下&#65292;思想空前一致&#65292;執行力行動力必然大幅度提高&#65292;對於中華民族偉大復興&#65292;對於實現兩個</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">100</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">年奮鬥目標&#65292;有百利而無一害&#12290;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">實行了終身制&#65292;砸爛了貞潔牌坊&#65292;從今往後堂堂正正搞獨裁&#65292;理直氣壯依法治國&#65292;想抓誰就抓誰&#65292;陰謀家野心家&#65292;貪污腐敗&#65292;黑社會分子&#65292;各種罪名應有盡有&#12290;一人治國是摒棄消滅官僚主義的最有力的武器&#12290;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">實行了終身制&#65292;全黨服從一人&#65292;沒有了派系之爭&#12290;全軍服從一人&#65292;沒有了政變可能&#12290;全民服從一人&#65292;人人都是向陽花&#12290;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">有人見到終身制就想起獨裁&#65292;害怕對人民實行恐怖政策&#65292;其實&#65292;中國歷史上的明君&#12289;聖君&#12289;開國之君&#12289;中興之君&#65292;哪一位又不是獨裁者呢&#65311;獨裁者也能興旺國家造福人民&#12290;反之&#65292;非獨裁者也可以給國家百姓帶來空前災難&#12290;所以獨裁不獨裁不是問題的根源&#65292;而是由誰來擔當獨裁者&#65292;這才是問題的核心&#12290;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">聽說川普總統非常羨慕我的終身制&#12290;我只能勸他說&#65292;貪心不足蛇吞象&#12290;就你這德行臨時起意能撈個總統當當&#65292;上帝夠眷顧你了&#12290;我可是從縣委書記起&#65292;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">30</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">年兢兢業業&#65292;一步一步地走到今天的&#12290;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">詩曰&#65306;向天再借</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">500</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">年&#65292;我卻只要</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">50</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">年&#12290;至少</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">2049</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">年&#65292;</span><span .="line-height: 115%;">31</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">年不過份&#12290;</span></span></div>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>
