<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">習&#65306;&#8220;為何不能&#65311;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">何&#65306;&#8220;您會累死&#12290;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">習&#65306;&#8220;再累心也甜&#12290;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">何&#65306;&#8220;那您也不能這麼做&#12290;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">習&#65306;&#8220;又為何不能&#65311;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">何&#65306;&#8220;人家會說您想搞獨裁&#12290;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">習&#65306;&#8220;我搞獨裁&#65311;搞獨裁我就連任四屆&#12290;連任三屆算什麼獨裁&#65311;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">何&#65306;&#8220;連任三屆算半吊子獨裁&#12290;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">習&#65306;&#8220;半吊子獨裁算不算獨裁&#65311;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
