<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">習&#65306;&#8220;白馬當然是馬&#12290;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
