<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">何&#65306;&#8220;對&#65292;乾脆改成終身制&#65292;反正天下人都知道您要搞獨裁&#12290;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
<div .="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Tahoma, Arial, Helvetica, snas-serif; font-size: 14px;">
<span style="font-size: medium;"><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">習&#65306;&#8220;可我有點害羞&#65292;還有點擔心&#12290;是誰把那條</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;" lang="ZH-CN">&nbsp;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">&#8216;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">连续任职不得超过两届</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: 宋体;" lang="ZH-CN">&#8217;寫進憲法的&#65311;&#8221;</span><span .="line-height: 115%; font-family: &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif;"></span></span></div>
